PrincipalValueCollection<T> Class

In this Article

Multi-valued properties, such as stem.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.AuthenticablePrincipal.PermittedWorkstations*, have a value of the type PrincipalValueCollection(T). This class provides methods to enumerate and manipulate those values.
